quran[49]{c,v,t}:
  50,27,"Umhlobo wakhe (uSathana) uya kuthi: “Nkosi yethu, asindim owamenza ukuba abe ngumgabadeli koko nguye ngokwakhe owaba sekulahlekeni (okwambeka) kude.”"
  50,28,"(UAllâh) Uya kuthi: “Musani ukuphikisana phambi kwaM, ekubeni Ndandinilumkisile kwangenxa engaphambili.”"
  50,29,Ilizwi (elingummiselo) aliyi kuguqulwa kuM yaye Andisokuze Ndibe ngumsweli bulungisa kwizicaka
  50,30,"NgeMini eSiya kuthi esiHogweni: “Ingaba ugcwele? Siya (kuphendula) sona sithi: “Ingaba kusekho abanye na?”"
  50,31,"Ke kaloku iPaladesi iya kusondezwa kubenzi bokulungileyo, ingabi kude"
  50,32,"(Kuya kuthiwa): “Oku koko nanithenjiswe ngako (oko) kokwakhe wonke ongumbuyeli kuAllâh nomgcini womnqophiso waKhe"
  50,33,"Owamoyikayo uSozinceba, Ongabonwayo, wabuyela (kuYe) ngentliziyo (enenguquko)"
  50,34,Ngena kuyo (iPaladesi) ngoxolo. Le yiMini yaphakade.”
  50,35,"Baya kufumana konke abakunqwenelayo apho, yaye kuThi kusekho nokunye okungaphaya koko"
  50,36,"Kanti zingaphi izizukulwana eSazitshabalalisayo ngaphambili kunabo, ezazinkulu kunabo ngamandla zityhutyhe ilizwe lonke, ikhona phofu indawo yokubalekela"
  50,37,Inene kuko oko kukho inkumbuzo kuye nabani na ophulaphulayo lo gama ekho (ngokwasengqondweni)
  50,38,Sawadala ngenene amazulu nomhlaba noko kuphakathi kuwo ngeentsuku ezintandathu kwaye akukho kudinwa kwaSichukumisayo
  50,39,"Ke wena yiba nomonde ngoko bakutshoyo, uzukise (uAllâh) ngendumiso yeNkosi yakho phambi kokuphuma kwelanga naphambi kokutshona kwalo"
  50,40,(Nakwinxalenye) yobusuku. Mzukise nasemva kokuqubuda (emthandazweni)
  50,41,Ke kaloku uphulaphule ngeMini xa uMmemezi eya kumemeza kwindawo ekufuphi
  50,42,NgeMini abaya kuva isithonga ngenyaniso. Leyo yiMini yokuphuma (emangcwabeni)
  50,43,Inene Sithi abanika ubomi Senze nokufa yaye kuThi kulapho kuza kuphelelwa khona
  50,44,NgeMini umhlaba uya kuzahlukanisa nabo (baze baphume emangcwabeni abo) ngesaquphe; olo luqokelelo olulula kuThi
  50,45,"Sikwazi kakuhle abakuthethayo, yaye wena awungomnyanzelisi phezu kwabo (wokubenza bakholwe ngenkani) kodwa ke wena khumbuza nge’Kur’ân nabani na lowo usoyikayo isilumkiso saM"
  51,1,Ndifunga (ngeMimoya) evuthuzayo
  51,2,(Nangamafu) athwala umthwalo onzima wamanzi
  51,3,Nangee(nqanawa) eziwiza kalula nangocoselelo
  51,4,Nangezo (ngelosi) zahlulahlula (izinto) ngokomyalelo (ka- Allâh)
  51,5,Inene oko nithenjiswe ngako kuyinyaniso
  51,6,Kananjalo inene imbuyekezo iza kwenzeka
  51,7,Ndifunga nangamazulu aneendlela
  51,8,Inene nina nahlukile ngeentetho
  51,9,"Olahlekileyo\twakude\tkuyo\t(i’Kur’ân)\tngulowo ulahlekisiweyo"
  51,10,Abatshabalalayo ngamaxoki
  51,11,Abaphantsi kwesigqubuthelo bengenanyameko
  51,12,"Bayabuza, “Inini na iMini yembuyekezo?”"
  51,13,(Leyo) yiMini abaya kujingiswa ngayo eMlilweni
  51,14,"(Kananjalo kuza kuthiwa kubo): “Ngcamlani isohlwayo senu ke. Oku koko naningenamonde ngako.”"
  51,15,Inene wona amalungisa aya kuba phakathi kweMiyezo nemithombo
  51,16,Esamkela oko iNkosi yawo Iwanike kona. Kaloku wona aye aba ngabenzi bokulungileyo kwangaphambili
  51,17,Wona ayelala kancinane ebusuku
  51,18,Nangeeyure eziphambi konyezi ayeye acele itarhu (kuAllâh)
  51,19,"Kantinasebutyebinibawo(kwakuyekukhutshwe) amalungelo (abahlwempuzekileyo), abangqibi nababandazelekileyo"
  51,20,Ke kaloku emhlabeni kukho imiqondiso kwabanyanisekileyo (elukholweni)
  51,21,Nakuni buqu. Kanti aniboni na
  51,22,Nasezulwini kukho imbonelelo yenu yako konke enithenjiswe ngako
  51,23,"Ke kaloku (Ndifunga) ngeNkosi yamazulu nomhlaba, inene yona (i’Kur’ân) yinyaniso enjengokuba nithetha"
  51,24,Ingaba ibali leendwendwe ezixabisekileyo zikaIbrâhîm lifikile na kuwe
  51,25,"Ekungeneni kwazo emzini wakhe zathi: “(Siya nibulisa) ngoxolo. Waphendula yena, (nakuni makube) luxolo, nina ningabantu abangaziwayo.”"
  51,26,Wahamba waya kusapho lwakhe wabuya nenyama yethole elityetyisiweyo elojiweyo
  51,27,"Walibeka phambi kwazo (iindwendwe ezo); wathi: “Aniyi kutya na?”"
  51,28,"Waziva enokuzoyika. Zathi zona: “Ungoyiki,” zamnika iindaba ezivuyisayo zenkwenkwana enolwazi"
  51,29,"Ke kaloku umkakhe weza kuye ngesikhalo (somothuko) ezibetha ubuso bakhe, esithi: “(Mna ndingumfazi) oludlolwazana nje!”"
  51,30,"Zathi zona: Itsho njalo ke iNkosi yakho; inene yona nguSolubabalo, uSolwazi"